B044C007V031	44	7	31	And Moses seeing it, admired the vision: and as he drew near to behold it, the voice of the Lord came to him, saying,
B044C007V032	44	7	32	«I am the God of your fathers, the God of Abraham, and the God of Isaac, and the God of Jacob.» 'And Moses trembled, and did not dare to behold it.'
B044C007V033	44	7	33	«And the Lord said to him,» 'Loose your shoes from your feet; for the place in which you stand is holy ground.'
B044C007V034	44	7	34	«I have surely seen the evil treatment of my people, which are in Egypt, and I have heard their groaning, and I am come down to deliver them; and now, come, I send you into Egypt.»
