B044C013V038	44	13	38	Be it known, therefore, to you, brethren, that by Him remission of sins is proclaimed to you:
B044C013V039	44	13	39	and by Him, every one that believes is justified from all things; from which you could not be justified by the law of Moses.
B044C013V040	44	13	40	See to it, therefore, that what is spoken in the prophets may not come upon you:
B044C013V041	44	13	41	«Behold, you despisers, and wonder, and perish: for I perform a work in your days; a work which you will not believe, though one should distinctly declare it to you.»
B044C013V042	44	13	42	Now, when going out, they requested that these words might be spoken to them, on the following Sabbath.
