B044C015V041	44	15	41	And he went through Syria and Cilicia confirming the congregations;
B044C016V001	44	16	1	and came to Derbe and Lystra; and, behold, a certain disciple was there, whose name was Timothy, the son of a believing Jewess, but of a Grecian father;
B044C016V002	44	16	2	who had an honorable character given by the brethren in Lystra and Iconium.
