B044C016V012	44	16	12	and came thence to Philippi, which is a city of the first part of Macedonia, a colony: and we continued in this city for some days.
B044C016V013	44	16	13	And on the Sabbath day we went out of the city to the side of the river, according to the custom, where was an oratory; and sitting down, we spoke to the women that were assembled there.
