B044C016V016	44	16	16	Now it came to pass, that as we were going to the oratory, we were met by a certain maid-servant that had a spirit of divination, who brought her owners much gain by prophesying:
B044C016V017	44	16	17	the same, following after Paul and us, cried out, These men are the servants of the Most High God, who declare to you the way of salvation.
B044C016V018	44	16	18	And this she did for several days. But Paul, being grieved, turned and said to the spirit, I charge you, in the name of Jesus Christ, to go out of her. And it went out that very hour.
