B044C017V001	44	17	1	And taking their journey through Amphipolis and Apollonia, they came to Thessalonica; where there was a synagogue of the Jews.
B044C017V002	44	17	2	And according to Paul's custom, he entered in among them, and discoursed to them for three Sabbaths from the scriptures;
B044C017V003	44	17	3	opening them, and evidently showing that the Messiah ought to suffer, and to rise from the dead; and that this is the Messiah, even Jesus, whom I declare to you.
