B044C017V007	44	17	7	and Jason has privately received them. And all these men act contrary to the decrees of Cesar, saying that there is another king, one Jesus.
B044C017V008	44	17	8	And they alarmed the multitude and the magistrates of the city, when they heard these things.
B044C017V009	44	17	9	And having taken security of Jason, and the rest, they dismissed them.
