B044C017V031	44	17	31	because he has appointed a day, in which he will judge the world righteously, by that Man whom he has ordained: of which he has given assurance to all men, by raising him from the dead.
B044C017V032	44	17	32	And when they heard of the resurrection of the dead, some made a jest of it, and others said, We will hear you again upon this subject.
