B044C019V015	44	19	15	But the evil spirit answering, said, Jesus I know, and Paul I know; but who are you?
B044C019V016	44	19	16	And the man in whom the evil spirit was, sprung upon them, and getting master of them prevailed against them, so that they fled out of the house, naked and wounded.
