B044C026V019	44	26	19	From that time, King Agrippa, I was not disobedient to the heavenly vision:
B044C026V020	44	26	20	but declared, first to them at Damascus, and at Jerusalem, and through all the country of Judea; and then to the Gentiles, that they should reform, and return to God, performing deeds worthy of reformation.
