B044C026V023	44	26	23	that the Messiah would be a sufferer-would be first of a resurrection from the dead-would give light to the people, and to the Gentiles.
B044C026V024	44	26	24	And as he was thus making his defense, Festus said, with a loud voice, Paul, you are distracted: much learning drives you to madness.
