B066C018V001	66	18	1	And after this, I saw an angel descending from heaven, who had great power; and the earth was enlightened with his glory.
B066C018V002	66	18	2	And he cried with a mighty and a loud voice, saying, It is fallen! it is fallen! it is fallen! even Babylon the Great: and it is become the habitation of demons, and the hold of every unclean spirit, and a cage of every unclean and hateful bird:
