B066C018V006	66	18	6	Give her, as he also has given; and recompense to her double, according to her works: in the cup which she has mingled, mingle to her double.
B066C018V007	66	18	7	In proportion to the degree in which she has made ostentation of her glory, and lived in luxury, inflict upon her torment and grief. Because she has said in her heart, I sit as a queen, and am not a widow, and shall not see sorrow;
